file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: '{{title}}'
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  '/unordered-params/{path_param}':
    get:
      summary: Mixed parameters in swagger definition
      operationId: fakeapi.hello.unordered_params_response
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
      parameters:
        - name: first
          in: query
          description: First Param
          schema:
            type: integer
        - name: path_param
          in: path
          required: true
          description: Path Param
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: second
          in: query
          description: Second Param
          schema:
            type: integer
servers:
  - url: /v1.0
